snippet.title: HITMAN World of Assassination - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome the World of Assassination. Everything HITMAN under one roof. Travel to 21 exotic sandbox locations, experience a rich story campaign, new ways to play and more.

HITMAN World of Assassination is out now! https://ioi.dk/hitman
